watchcat
---------------------------
Post photos taken by motion(*), and delete photos from Picasa.
"watchcat" is the name that is I monitor for my pet cat.

 * http://motion.sf.net
 

INSTALL:

1. Install Debian package googlecl, motion.
   $ sudo apt-get install googlecl motion

2. Setting motion
   $ sudo vi /etc/default/motion
   --
   -start_motion_daemon=no
   +start_motion_daemon=yes
   --

   $ sudo vi /etc/motion/motion.conf
   --
   -daemon off
   +daemon on
   -setup_mode off
   +setup_mode on
   -snapshot_interval 0
   +snapshot_interval 1800
   -; text_left CAMERA %t
   +text_left CAMERA %t
   -target_dir /tmp/motion
   +target_dir /var/local/motion

3. register crontab entry.
   $ crontab -e
   --
   3-59/15 * * * * ~/postphoto.sh
   8-59/15 * * * * ~/deletephoto.sh

 -- Kouhei Maeda <mkouhei at palmtb.net>, Mon, 25 Apr 2011 22:04:15 +0900
